Package com.oracle.tools.runtime.java.virtualization

Interface Summary
VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder.ConnectorFactory A JMXConnectorFactory defines factory methods to acquire JMX Connectors for clients and servers.
VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder.RmiRegistryFactory A VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder.RmiRegistryFactory provides the ability to create Rmi Registrys.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDelegatingOutputStream An AbstractDelegatingOutputStream is a FilterOutputStream that delegates output to an appropriate VirtualizedSystem OutputStream.
DelegatingMBeanServer A DelegatingMBeanServer is an MBeanServer implementation that delegates calls to the appropriate MBeanServer of a VirtualizedSystem.
DelegatingMBeanServerBuilder A DelegatingMBeanServerBuilder is an MBeanServerBuilder that delegates requests onto the appropriate VirtualizedSystem MBeanServerBuilder.
DelegatingProperties A DelegatingProperties is a Properties implementation that delegates Properties method calls onto appropriate VirtualizedSystem.getProperties().
DelegatingStdErrOutputStream A DelegatingStdErrOutputStream is an AbstractDelegatingOutputStream implementation for the StdErr OutputStream of a VirtualizedSystem.
DelegatingStdOutOutputStream A DelegatingStdOutOutputStream is an AbstractDelegatingOutputStream implementation for the StdOut OutputStream of a VirtualizedSystem.
LineNumberingOutputStream A LineNumberingOutputStream is an OutputStream that numbers each new line as it is output.
Virtualization The Virtualization class provides helpers to establish and dismantal System virtualizations.
VirtualizationClassLoader A VirtualizationClassLoader is a VirtualizedSystemClassLoader that uses the child-first / parent-last strategy for resolving and loading classes.
VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder A VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder is an MBeanServerBuilder that isolates MBeanServers with in a VirtualizedSystem.
VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder.DefaultConnectorFactory The default implementation of the VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder.ConnectorFactory.
VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder.DefaultRmiRegistryFactory The default implementation of an VirtualizedMBeanServerBuilder.RmiRegistryFactory.
VirtualizedSystem A VirtualizedSystem encapsulates state and functionality typically defined by the Java System class.
VirtualizedSystemClassLoader A VirtualizedSystemClassLoader is a URLClassLoader that defines a VirtualizedSystem, that of which is used to encapsulate and isolate System-level resources for classes loaded with the said ClassLoader.
